--
-- WHY THIS EXISTS
-- Migration 0055 DROPped the old public.trips + public.lorries TABLES in favour
-- of scm.*. Two compatibility VIEWs (public.trips / public.lorries over scm.*)
-- were then created OUT-OF-BAND to keep legacy callers working — they exist in
